data.description: Cozy Cottage style home featuring: Bedrooms: It has three bedrooms, which can accommodate a family or provide extra space for guests or home office needs.  Bathrooms: The house has two bathrooms, one of which is the master bathroom. The master bathroom is designed like a spa retreat and includes double sinks and a soaker tub for relaxation.  Garage: There's a two-car garage, providing ample parking and storage space.  Lot Size: The property is situated on a partially fenced lot, which may offer space for outdoor activities, gardening, or other uses. There are some repairs needed from the Hurricanes/freeze making this home a value! All measurements more or less.
